The evidence with the title 'Fact-checking the second Clinton-Trump debate - Chicago Tribune ' says Oct 9, 2016  ... CLINTON : "we are now, for the first time ever, energy independent." THE facts: Clinton overstates the case . For the first time in decades the United States gets more energy domestically than it imports , but it is not yet entirely energy independent . Oil still is imported, from the Mideast and elsewhere. 
